title: Chile GDP Constant Prices
description: GDP Constant Prices in Chile decreased to 51710.06 CLP Billion in the second quarter of 2022 from 51713.70 CLP Billion in the first quarter of 2022. GDP Constant Prices in Chile averaged 27622.96 CLP Billion from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 52006.92 CLP Billion in the fourth quarter of 2021 and a record low of 13802 CLP Billion in the first quarter of 1996. This page provides - Chile GDP Constant Prices - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Central Bank Of Chile
